name: Tandoori Flames Indian Restaurant
description: Tandoori Flames is a Indian restaurant
overview: Tandoori Flames invite you to relax and enjoy The unique Flavours of India .Over several years Tandoori Flames - Indian Restaurant Melbourne has gained lots of popularity by providing Tradional Indian Food & good customer service .Ideally located in the heart of Hobson’s bay Melbourne ( 10 minutes from Melbourne CBD)offers unique dining experience. Tandoori flames - Indian Restaurant present constantly evolving menu and carefully matched wine list. Tandoori flames designed all this to reflect an ethos of innovation and creativity at Tandoori flames we are recreating some of the finest curries (Indian food) from the royal courts of India. We use finest quality ingredients in all our cooking which make you visiting back to us again & again. We assure you our food taste till last bite
